                   and Co. of 127 l. 11 s. 7 d. and unlawfully divising to fraud the said Messrs. Payne and Co. afterwards; (to wit) on the said 2d day of June, did feloniously make, forge, and counterfeit, on the back of the said parchment instrument, and under the said order, a certain acquittance and receipt for money, with the name 
                     <persName id="t17921031-56-person548">
                        George
                         Smith
                     <interp inst="t17921031-56-person548" type="surname" value="Smith"></interp>
