                  , and partner, for the said sum
            </rs>; the tenor of which receipt is as follow:</p>
               <p>'Received by me the 2d of June, 1792,</p>
               <p>'for partners and self, George Smith,' with intention to defraud them.</p>
               <p>A second count, charging him with uttering the like instrument with the like intention.</p>
               <p>A third and fourth counts, for the same offence, with intent to defraud 
               
                  <persName id="t17921031-56-victim552" type="victimName">
                     Augustus 
                     Pechell
                  <interp inst="t17921031-56-victim552" type="surname" value="Pechell"></interp>
